      "title": "Risks, costs, and the expected complication of re-injury",
      "abstract": "BACKGROUND: The purpose of this study was to determine the characteristics of young victims of violence and the risk of rehospitalization due to intentional injury (recidivism) and to estimate the potential cost of these injuries. MATERIALS AND METHODS: Trauma admissions from January 1, 1991 to December 31, 1993, at San Francisco General Hospital of youths Language: en"
